This dataset is provided "AS IS" without warranty of any kind, either expressed or implied. The project maintainers have made reasonable efforts to comply with all applicable licenses, but users are responsible for ensuring their own compliance when using or distributing this data.

本資料集按「現狀」提供，不提供任何明示或暗示的保證。專案維護者已盡合理努力遵守所有適用授權，但使用者應自行確保其使用或散佈資料時的合規性。

